.org/epig10002085\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002085\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650789\" target=\"_blank\">7277\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bivona 1970 19 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":243,"html":244},"handnote"," \u003Cp>Tall and very narrow letters, fairly crudely carved, with AV in ligature.\u003C/p> Line 1  105  Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":246,"html":247},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[249,251,254,256,259,260,263,264],{"html":250},"Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Jonathan Prag",{"id":252,"lang":124,"html":253},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"imperial\" data-text=\"Imperatori · Caesari · Marco · Aurelio\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Imperatori\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"imperator\">Imp(eratori?)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Caesari\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Caesari\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Caesar\">Caes(ari?)\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Marco\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Marco\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Marcus\">M(arco?)\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aurelio\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Aurelio\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Aurelius\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">